description:
Microsoft Team Foundation Server Client

Integrate with Team Foundation Server 2015 and Visual Studio Team Services from desktop-based, ASP.NET, and other Windows applications.  Provides access to version control, work item tracking, build, and more via public REST APIs.
releaseNotes:
14.95.x correlates to Visual Studio 2015 Update 2.  
14.95.1 correlates to Visual Studio 2015 Update 2 RC1, or TFS 2015 Update 2 RC2.  
Portable and NetCore binaries will remain in Preview, throughout Visual Studio 2015. 

14.95.2 is a packaging change only, and addresses an issue installing the package in UAP projects.
title: Microsoft Team Foundation Server Client
